data.description: Welcome to the stunning former model home for Deerlake!  You’ll enjoy all the builder extras to include extensive, gorgeous trim work and molding, smooth ceilings & recessed lighting thru-out!  Light & bright on all levels!  Custom leaded glass front door, sidelights & transom!  Luxurious Primary Suite on main with double-tray ceiling, spa retreat Bath, large walk-in shower with pebble reflexology floor, Kohler designer extra large soaking tub, double vanity & 2 walk-in Closets with shelving!  Beautiful hardwood floors on main & custom Italian porcelain tile on terrace level!  Amazing terrace level offers a custom built, incredible approx. 850 bottle Wine Cellar with custom granite pouring/tasting station, Kitchen, Full Bath, billiard table & fireplace all open to your covered patio!  Main Kitchen offers a wine fridge, a NEW Refrigerator, granite countertops, double deep sinks, large walk-in pantry & has an open layout!  2-story foyer & Living Rm with gorgeous fireplace impress the best!  Conversation Rm/Office off foyer w/Built-ins!  Ensuite BR upstairs with 2 additional BRs with walk-in closets!  NEW roof in 2022!  Freshly refinished 2-car garage flooring with wainscoting, insulated door & “quiet” Belt-Drive Lift Master opener with “MyQ” Smart App Technology!  Wrap-around large driveway to 3rd car oversized garage for tandem parking, large enough for boat, etc. & has a built-in workshop!  Generous closets & storage throughout to include 2 attic access points!  Intercom system with radio thru-out!  Freshly stained deck with downlights & NEW mulch & pine straw!  Inground irrigation system in front and back!  This beautiful home is hard-coat stucco!  Deerlake has a gated entry and offers state-of-the-art community amenities that include Clubhouse, Olympic-size pool, fun children’s pool, 6 tennis/pickleball courts, basketball, Tot Lot, golf cart parking, gorgeous lake with fountain and fishing pier!  Close to tons of shops & restaurants!  This special home has it all!
